OL,3,CMan arrested in relation to report of
OL,4,Cracist abuse during Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FA man has been arrested in relation to
OL,7,Fa report of racist abuse during the
OL,8,FTyne-Wear derby.
OL,10,FThe 45-year-old was arrested on
OL,11,FTuesday (1 April) on suspicion of a
OL,12,Fracially-aggravated public order
OL,13,Foffence.
OL,15,FReferee Anthony Taylor was made aware
OL,16,Fof an incident by the Sunderland
OL,17,Fcaptain during the game against
OL,18,FNewcastle Untied at St James' Park on
OL,19,F22 March.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
