OL,3,CMan arrested in relation to report of
OL,4,Cracist abuse during Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FThe Premier League's anti-
OL,7,Fdiscrimination protocol was initiated,
OL,8,Fwith both sets of coaching teams
OL,9,Fconsulted before play eventually
OL,10,Fresumed.
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police said the man from
OL,13,Fthe Gateshead area has since been
OL,14,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,15,Fenquiries.
